    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting with my trusty car, and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, perfect for zipping around town or heading out on a road trip. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
