    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. It is equipped with a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and the factory variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been completed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The rod bearings have also been addressed, providing peace of mind for high-revving performance. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the mechanical components are dialed in, with refreshed suspension bushings and a crisp shift linkage that preserves the chassis\u2019s legendary telepathic handling.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Ready for sale.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
